Class DiscountCategory

  • java.lang.Object
    • common.DiscountCategory

  • final class DiscountCategory
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines Discount Approval Request (DAR) discount categories. Defines all discount categories, each of which is comprised of a DiscountCategoryCode value, name, Total Discount percentage and dollar amount thresholds, and Additional Discount routing table
    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Jeffrey Blaze
    See Also:
    DiscountCategoryCode, ApprovalChain
